node.text:
What a sick day of riding bikes in one of the most picturesque trails in the world with such a sick crew. Thanks to all those who showed up at the second stop of Fox #HitThePark at @verbierbikepark and helped make this event a success. A special thanks to @farinet_verbier for the warm welcome 🙏

@andreulacondeguy @lluislacondeguy @peferry @jerome_caroli @les_9_roues @gemmacorbera @lauriegreenland_ 🔥
